{"tid":561253,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[休班警GOAL [警超聯 ]男警涉以假牌佔用電單車位 重案組接手查","createTime":"2018-02-15T00:22:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-15T13:29:29.000Z","uid":51271,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"29d4be4c6afe6e14097fd44f498b820f1a3e5bc3","tid":561253,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T00:22:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180214/57834731\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180214%2F57834731&d=tC8wHLE06i9okBTfUkldoiwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=2ee7e66e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180214%2F57834731&h=ca5c6141\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180214/57834731</a><br />\n<br />\n一名41歲姓吳的男警務人員，涉嫌於上月15日在香港仔分區一停車場，以虛假車牌使用一電單車月租停車位。港島總區刑事部人員經深入調查後，於昨日把他拘捕。他涉嫌以欺騙手段取得財產，已獲准保釋候查，須於2月下旬向警方報到，案件由港島總區重案組跟進。<br />\n<br />\n<em><span style=\"color: red;\">下刪十數字</span></em><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e0e6623913c656c716f7aad4cf1a0f1f2314ffb","tid":561253,"uid":7439,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T13:29:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.makeagif.com/media/1-19-2018/eTdQIJ.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.makeagif.com%2Fmedia%2F1-19-2018%2FeTdQIJ.gif&h=ce4debb9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n入球球員：🇧🇷費蘭度(傑志)<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">2018-02-20(下周二、年初五)20:00 亞冠盃 傑志 vs 全北汽車(韓國)\t@香港大球場</span>"}]}